---
title: Pho with Tofu
description: This classic Vietnamese soup will warm your belly this winter. In our version, we’ve added pillowy silken tofu. Garlic, ginger, and mint create a fragrant broth, and bok choy adds a splash of color. Have your own chopsticks? Now’s the time to use them to slurp up all those delicious rice noodles!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d2243f6ced6e52798b4568.jpg
